About 8a.nu

8a.nu is on of the world's largest climbing communities and news sites with over 70000 members using it to keep their climbing log.

8a.nu was opened in 1999 by Jens Larssen as a local sport climbing site for Gothenburg - Sweden. The idea of a community site and logbook to keep track of climbs immediately appealed to climbers from all over the world and soon many of the world’s best were using it. Since 2017, 8a.nu has been part of Vertical-Life, with Jens Larssen as the editor-in-chief.
